Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.10,0:00:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.94,0:00:19.81,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.88,0:00:23.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.81,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.89,0:00:32.31,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.56,0:00:41.33,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:50.40,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.97,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:56.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.79,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.86,0:01:07.56,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.10,0:01:16.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.03,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.11,0:01:23.30,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.38,0:01:24.47,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.22,0:01:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼煩惱嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.56,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.53,0:01:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為從我們的角度來看\N一直以為妳就像神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我聽聽妳的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個東西想讓妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於我們的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.48,0:02:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#14 失去的五重奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守護者，你想去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.29,0:02:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得想個辦法讓賽內絲\N開動這艘船才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天殺一千人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你為這點小事動搖\N我可就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會受不了\N有很多人因為自己而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情真是個麻煩的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.04,0:02:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要煩惱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽...媽媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷神之錘啊，攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的決心還真是堅定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現的可是妳父親耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親已經不在這個世上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦拭冰冷遺體的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火葬時點火的人也是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶還沒有模糊到\N會被這種幻影所騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我們被留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔莉他們有可能想對\N夏儂和帕希菲卡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個凡人\N留到最後再處理，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先到中樞部去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動這台史基特是第一優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凡人就用凡人的方法表現自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要到王都去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.34,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算平安到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到王都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小史比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會逃到基亞特去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克樞機卿，我遵從了神諭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令處死剛出生的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王上\N這些事瑪烏傑魯神統統知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.13,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是命運之日一刻一刻地接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主毀滅世界的那個日子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加快動作就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加快動作...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把廢棄公主...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基亞特的船侵犯我國領海的事\N大家都知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我還聽說緋紅\N和廢棄公主接觸過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.93,0:04:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有廢棄公主是不是\N和基亞特軍勾結要攻打萊邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這只是謠傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，火藥味越來越重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.50,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說王國軍也接到\N由國王親自下達的旨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容是傾全軍之力殺掉廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果殺死在基亞特手中的公主\N可就會演變成戰爭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，吉兒的預知裡\N好像也看到令人不放心的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定王國軍會使用那個魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個魔法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,條約中所禁止的\N長距離戰略級攻性魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基亞特帝國...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個國家的技術\N和軍事力量弄到手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有吸引力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個國家的領土也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.34,0:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當想要的東西自己送上門時\N當然得搶下來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確，現在是絕佳的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你有那個不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長距離戰略級攻性魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"奈落"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍，您怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了向妳說明\N我重新組成的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你們稱為星空的領域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前人類曾擁有\N到達這個空間的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.68,0:05:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是有一天\N人類的面前出現了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個敵人不知來自宇宙的何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在還不清楚理由的狀況之下\N就開始攻擊人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛羅蒂也說過這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為這些只不過是神話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個敵人是跟人類\N不同的智慧生物...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將其稱為"H．l"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類和H．l的戰爭持續了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此人類創造了我們龍機神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有如同神一般的力量\N最強並且是最終武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們被稱為"最後的魔獸"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.73,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是控制我們龍機神的人工智慧\N在設計上有缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持續出現承受不了高度複雜程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因而半途產生異變的龍機神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200台量產型當中\N174台無法運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.58,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它26台雖然好不容易\N避免了人工智慧的失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.22,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為了以防萬一\N設下了非常嚴格的防護措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有其駕駛\N也就是龍騎士的許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.39,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了自衛之外\N九成的戰鬥用程式都不能執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽，我在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.81,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，由於我們無法正常運作\N所以被分配去打區域戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.55,0:07:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又投入了我們的改良型\N完全獨立運作的戰天使型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是戰天使型遭到敵人洗腦\N倒戈相向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是現在的秩序守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.39,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們原本是站在我們這一邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的背叛導致我方敗北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來秩序守護者就擔任起\N管理人類的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我原本的主人，貝克納姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲，對不起，我已經沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳陪我一起作戰至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.99,0:08:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你願意接受我\N我才能存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你毫不畏懼的接受我\N我才不至於像妹妹們那樣損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去你，我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲，拜託妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這會讓妳背負殘酷的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，妳要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.05,0:08:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用妳的力量幫助我們\N遙遠未來的子孫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝克納姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.12,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要，我不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵從已故主人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待我應該幫助的人出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因為主人如此期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳當時在湖上見到的就是\N失去主人之龍機神的悲慘下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至今一直把你們當作\N完成自身使命的棋子和道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥也是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道為什麼\N我無法對你們的期望視而不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.88,0:09:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有根據，但是我覺得\N這樣會背叛我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量能在一瞬間\N毀滅大量的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以靠自己單獨的判斷行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以長久以來\N我沒有自己做過決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有決定的權限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.86,0:10:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是由我的主人決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那個人已經不在世上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.74,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是夏儂哥現在\N不是賽菲莉絲的主人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂大概不會相信我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我的真面目之後\N仍然不感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.68,0:10:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟我原本的主人一樣地對待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔莉開始對夏儂洗腦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗腦？為了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的是讓他變成一個\N即使犧牲王都數百萬的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.88,0:10:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了保護妳\N便不會感到任何痛苦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她跌落到谷底前\N好不容易才用魔法救了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經是個\N能獨當一面的宮廷魔法師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.44,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是比不上凱洛兒大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是早點回去比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連名字都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我知道夏儂\N或是拉蔻兒會被殺害的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會拋下一切保護他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有足夠的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是王妃殿下只有沉重的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被人知道她放走這個孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.94,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得幫這孩子取個名字才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是個大家都會喜歡的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.72,0:12:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得懂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代語？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這好像被稱為英語什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用緊急迴路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連接中樞機構動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YESor NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YES
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力恢復了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽內絲殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到妳真的動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經發揮效果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓守護者清楚自覺到\N他應該保護的是什麼才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是武器更是人類的僕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種做法違反我們的存在理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是只是個替代品而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的，帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸媽也是這麼希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔莉，妳做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是讓他看了過去的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他再次體認到\N妳的存在是無可替代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是連接到緊急迴路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓這個自由軌道要塞自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個要塞是妳的軀殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆也就意味著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最好的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點逃出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然為了到秩序守護者面前送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而乘坐這艘先驅者前往王都\N真是愚蠢至極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也在不斷地取回原本的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要順利逃走喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.51,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律法破壞者的力量\N還剩一千個小時就會發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多王都的人可能會被殺害\N怎麼可以就這樣逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對哥哥做這種奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓夏儂恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先逃出去比較要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦離開這個干涉力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再也無法解開洗腦的效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙已經是個廢人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲，我該怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能潛入他心裡去說服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是一個不小心\N妳的意識就會回不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這洗腦跟帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然能潛入人類的意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是無法干涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是一個步驟出錯，不僅守護者\N連律法破壞者都會失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望哥哥一直保持\N原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們成為了律法破壞者\N還有龍騎士這些我搞不懂的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.77,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想生為廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天幫忙做家事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟某個人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.61,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生兒育女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成老婆婆之後\N有一群兒孫圍繞身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.52,0:16:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的秘密\N我繼續不知道就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就沒有人會\N留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳說世界被封印住了\N可是我實在沒什麼感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.53,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使拿五千年以前的事情出來談\N我也完全搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.03,0:16:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚賽菲莉絲你們\N希望達成以前主人遺願的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很清楚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這對我們來說有什麼意義？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.02,0:16:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了，大概只有妳會這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了蛋包飯跟雞拼個你死我活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近老是輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也吃不到蛋包飯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.05,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.18,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.11,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是哥哥和姊姊的親妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有我是金頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到村裡的人都那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我的妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛說的人就讓他們去說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正帕希菲卡是我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望可以永遠這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是現在的生活，或是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，差不多該回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我還想跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，妳就多跟哥哥在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該回家囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我要跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.44,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，妳就跟哥哥在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的，我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害，哥哥好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少做這種噁心的事，行不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我好害怕喔\N這個怪小孩是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害，我最喜歡哥哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說很噁心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少給我那麼簡單就被洗腦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到現實世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼"咦"的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.37,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你平常都用什麼眼光來看我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然那麼簡單就解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這丫頭究竟是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.19,0:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來，只剩下\N跟秩序守護者開戰這條路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站好，站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進目標，萊邦王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有賽菲莉絲\N我哥哥才能恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了他的人是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如妳所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.99,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將你們牽扯進了我們的戰爭當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會很困擾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳道歉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:18.14,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.20,0:21:23.11,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.51,0:21:30.75,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.82,0:21:36.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.66,0:21:41.65,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.82,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.90,0:21:49.86,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.94,0:21:56.47,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.77,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.85,0:22:03.15,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.22,0:22:09.71,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.79,0:22:16.39,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.46,0:22:21.70,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.77,0:22:28.83,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡蘇魯三兄妹抱著必死的決心\N回到王都札威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是港口卻顯得十分安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國的將軍深信帕希菲卡他們\N所搭乘的要塞是侵略者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.99,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎開始在準備什麼危險的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在事情演變到不可收拾之前\N希望他們能先冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主下一回\N「力量與謀略的歌劇」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待